org.springframework.messaging.handler.invocation

接口 HandlerMethodArgumentResolver

  • 所有已知实现类:
    AbstractNamedValueMethodArgumentResolver, DestinationVariableMethodArgumentResolver, HandlerMethodArgumentResolverComposite, HeaderMethodArgumentResolver, HeadersMethodArgumentResolver, MessageMethodArgumentResolver, PayloadArgumentResolver, PrincipalMethodArgumentResolver

    public interface HandlerMethodArgumentResolver
    Strategy interface for resolving method parameters into argument values in the context of a given Message.
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      java.lang.Object resolveArgument(MethodParameter parameter, Message<?> message)
      Resolves a method parameter into an argument value from a given message.
      boolean supportsParameter(MethodParameter parameter)
      Whether the given method parameter is supported by this resolver.

    • 方法详细资料

      • supportsParameter

        boolean supportsParameter(MethodParameter parameter)
        Whether the given method parameter is supported by this resolver.
        参数:
        parameter - the method parameter to check
        返回:
        true if this resolver supports the supplied parameter; false otherwise

      • resolveArgument

        @Nullable
java.lang.Object resolveArgument(MethodParameter parameter,
                                            Message<?> message)
                                     throws java.lang.Exception
        Resolves a method parameter into an argument value from a given message.
        参数:
        parameter - the method parameter to resolve. This parameter must have previously been passed to supportsParameter(org.springframework.core.MethodParameter) which must have returned true.
        message - the currently processed message
        返回:
        the resolved argument value, or null
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - in case of errors with the preparation of argument values
